    "Indeed, both ChatGPT and GPT-4 were only trained on data up to September 2021 (23) and consequently have no knowledge of more recent developments.",
    "10.3389/fradi.2023.1224682",
    "In the realm of medical diagnostics, the potential for ChatGPT to misinterpret symptoms or overlook critical information could lead to diagnostic errors.",
    "For example, a patient may present with symptoms that align with multiple diagnoses.",
